{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_01","textHome":"是百江渚的说。虽然不知何故喜欢上了巧克力@，还穿上了围裙，但还是同样的小渚的说。@总之，看到这样的小渚，给点巧克力会很开@心的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_17","textHome":"作为巧克力甜点师的小渚，成为魔法少女时的@愿望，跟这个宇宙的小渚不太一样的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_18","textHome":"小渚向往自由的说。不管多么安全的地方，如@果连吃巧克力的自由都没有的话，小渚也要@谢绝的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_19","textHome":"突然冒出了新品巧克力的灵感的说！"}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_20","textHome":"巧克力甜点师的的水平提高了的说！"}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_21","textHome":"小渚还没有成为理想的自己的说。总有一天，@小渚要成为宇宙第一的巧克力甜点师的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_22","textHome":"小渚是为了自己而使用魔力的说。那就是小渚@来到地上的意义的说。至于宇宙变成什么样@都不要紧的说。啊……但如果宇宙都没有了@的话，就吃不到巧克力了的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_23","textHome":"其实小渚，是什么大人物的使者的说。然后现@在，比起使者还更高级了的说。但是，小渚@就是小渚的说。这份神奇的力量就要尽情浪@费的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_24","textHome":"今天也请多关照的说。因为小渚很自由，所以@没有什么计划的说。思考今天干什么的这段@时间，是小渚最喜欢的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_25","textHome":"早上了的说。在街上看到卖可爱的小刀的了，@所以准备去采购的说。之后就去麻美家打扰@，喝杯茶也不错的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.9,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_26","textHome":"午饭时间的说。今天吃的是巧克力甜甜圈和熔@岩巧克力蛋糕，喝的是热可可……不、不要@说全都是巧克力，的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_02","textHome":"请看的说！百江渚的新模样！没错的说……小@渚现在，是小小的巧克力甜点师的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":270000}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_27","textHome":"抱歉的说。现在不能分神的说。没错，对于巧@克力甜点师来说，现在就是准备明天的材料@的时间的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_28","textHome":"……呜啊……诶？嗯……几点了……的说？哈@……是小朋友……睡觉的时间的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_29","textHome":"并不是总想着制作甜点的说。没有变成穿围裙@的小渚的时候，还是和往常一样喜欢芝士的@小渚的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_30","textHome":"小渚有时候也会去消灭魔女的说。会用奶油袋@装饰得漂漂亮亮的，尽管出现的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":0}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界里多半藏着大秘密的说。小渚来到这@个世界的时候，也是在那间洋馆的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_32","textHome":"小渚的围裙也是战斗服的说。如果有需要小渚@的魔法少女的话，小渚就会伸出援手的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_33","textHome":"啊，什么事的说？小渚现在在考虑怎么做蛋白@脆饼的说。蛋白脆饼是各种甜点制作中的基@础的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_34","textHome":"停停，停下的说！不要摸摸头的说！小渚虽然@小，但也是成熟的甜点师的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_35","textHome":"小渚并不是脑子里100%都是吃的东西的说@！吃的东西……有、有70%左右的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_36","textHome":"小渚的梦想，是有一天能够戴上代表超一流的@巧克力甜点师的领巾的说。麻美也为小渚加@油的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_03","textHome":"是好久不见的见泷原的说。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_37","textHome":"情人节过后才是真正的战争的说。争夺打折促@销的巧克力这件事不能输给杏子的说。虽然@杏子和小渚一样都吃不来苦涩的纯巧克力的@说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_38","textHome":"虽然时不时会和沙耶香拌嘴的说。但是沙耶香@从来不会因为小渚年纪小就看不起小渚的说@。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":400}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":10.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_39","textHome":"焰去买用来制作送朋友的巧克力的材料了的说@。为了能够容错，买了一个人都抱不动那么@多的说。小渚觉得有点努力过头了的说。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_40","textHome":"遇到小圆的时候，有种以前在哪里遇见过的既@视感的说。也许在别的世界相遇过，并不是@什么奇怪的事情的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2700_00_41","textHome":"啊……是谁的说!?希望不要站在小渚背后的@说。还以为又是粉色的丘比，正想用危险的@魔法……啊啊，没事的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":270000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":270000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":270000,"motion":400}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":